&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">L7_WH_CTF/SRS/for_user via  v3.13.5
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">❯ cat flag_server.py | grep Layer7{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &amp;#39;flag&amp;#39;: &amp;#39;Layer7{ssrf_easy}&amp;#39;,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>문제 파일에 플래그가 하드코딩 되어있다.&lt;/p>
